## Quick commands

```bash
./setup-hermes.sh && source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip install -e ".[web-chat,platform]"
scripts/run_tests.sh tests/gateway/test_web_*.py tests/hermes_state/test_user_id_filtering.py
./startplatform.sh --host 127.0.0.1   # Platform SaaS（platform-api + gateway）
./startweb.sh --host 127.0.0.1        # Legacy key-only
cd web-chat && npm install && npm run build
```

## Before submitting changes

- [ ] Tests first — see `01-test-first.mdc`
- [ ] `scripts/run_tests.sh` green for touched areas
- [ ] No Hermes core edits outside Strategy 2 allowlist
- [ ] Per-user paths use `enter_user_context`
- [ ] No secrets in code/logs; keys encrypted at rest
- [ ] `TODOLIST.md` updated if completing a tracked task

User-facing replies: **中文**. Code identifiers & architecture terms: **English**.
